item.description:
The Vine in Plymouth, Court street, Sunday 6:00 to 9:00

Open mike night at the Vine Restaurant.... I'm looking for some people who want to enjoy some great live music while having a cocktail or two. I hear the food isn't too bad either. The music is live but not so loud that you can't carry on a good conversation. I hope to see you all there.

Look For Trisha (Tricia) with the brown scarf !!
